        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "רַבָּנַן: אֵין שׁוֹנִין קֶמַח בְּיוֹם טוֹב. מִשּׁוּם <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Pappeyas, third-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2534\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Pappeyas\" data-name-he=\"רבי פפייס\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-16687\">רַבִּי</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
