    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּיוֹם טוֹב. אֲמַר לְהוּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Naḥman bar Ya’akov, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2285\" data-full-name=\"Rav Naḥman bar Ya’akov\" data-name-he=\"רב נחמן בר יעקב\">רַב נַחְמָן</span>: פּוּקוּ וֶאֱמַרוּ לֵיהּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">לְאַבָּא</span>: שְׁקִילָא טֵיבוּתָךְ וְשַׁדְיָ[א] אַחִזְרֵי, פּוֹק חֲזִי",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כַּמָּה מַהוֹלָתָא הַדְרָן בִּנְהַרְדְּעָא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>דְּבֵיתְהוּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yosef I, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1764\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yosef I\" data-name-he=\"רב יוסף בר חייא\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-16693\">דְּרַב</span>",
